www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Justin-Timberlake-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Justin-Timberlake-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Justin-Timberlake-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Justin-Timberlake-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Justin-Timberlake-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/justin-timberlake">贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake)</a>宣布了他的专辑《Everything I Thought It Was》及其浪漫主打单曲《Selfish》。看看下面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/justin-timerlake-man-woods-review-2230941">贾斯汀·汀布莱克——《林中人》评论</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲标志着汀布莱克五年多来首次发行个人专辑。 《自私》由汀布莱克和路易斯·贝尔（<a href="/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>）、瑟库特（ <a href="/artists/maroon-5">Maroon 5</a> ）、塞隆·托马斯和艾米·艾伦（<a href="/artists/harry-styles">哈里·斯泰尔斯</a>）共同创作，歌词是： <em>“所以如果我嫉妒，我就无法控制/我想要你的每一点，我想我很自私/这对我的精神不好，但我无法抗拒，当/你像你一样在外面，但你无法隐藏它，不，”</em>描述一个对另一半神魂颠倒、全身心投入的情人。</p><p>由布拉德利·考尔德 (Bradley Calder) 执导，在这首歌的伴奏音乐视频中，这位《西装领带》歌手进入摄影棚的一扇小门，进入一条小走廊，在走廊里，他看起来像一个巨人，争先恐后地接听墙上的红色电话。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="贾斯汀·汀布莱克 - 自私（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/je0roKRn3nY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>汀布莱克最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-teases-new-album-everything-i-thought-it-was-previews-lead-single-selfish-3574177">于 1 月 19 日在家乡孟菲斯的欧菲姆剧院首次现场表演了《自私》</a> 。</p><p>在完成家乡演出后，汀布莱克还在 Instagram 上上传了他的专辑预告片的一部分。序言由演员本尼西奥·德尔·托罗 (Benicio del Toro) 旁白，描绘了一个加油站和汽车模型，JT 看着彩绘的日落。或者，正如德尔·托罗所叙述的那样：“他到底在盯着什么看？”</p><p>他即将发行的唱片《Everything I Thought It Was》将于 3 月 15 日通过 RCA 发行。您可以<a href="https://shop.justintimberlake.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订/预先保存。这是他自 2018 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/justin-timerlake-man-woods-review-2230941">《Man Of The Woods》以来的首张新专辑，</a> <em>NME</em>称其为“王牌”：“老汀布莱克在各个方面都闪闪发光 - 你知道吗？我们仍然认为他是王牌。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2aIoTBLJ4K/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113